CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 7, 1956, page 18, reads: "1. Lovely Mrs. Mabel B. Mills passes out delicious Nucoa tid-bits from the Best Foods Inc. Booth. Shown here with her is Best  Foods supervisor, Dan Gallagher"
TitMainTitle: Mabel B. Mills and Dan Gallagher standing in Best Foods Incorporated booth in Syria Mosque for the 1956 Pittsburgh Courier Home Service Fair
